[G, \lambda(G)] = \big\{ b^{-1} \cdot \lambda_a (b) \, \mid \, a, b \in G \big\} \subseteq \ker(\lambda).
\end{equation}
Moreover, if  $H_{\lambda}$ is a subgroup of $\Hol(G)$, then it is regular.

