The homomorphisms ${\alpha_n}:{C^{\rm R}_n(X)} \rightarrow {C^{\rm R}_n(X)}$
form a chain map ${\alpha}:{C^{\rm R}_*(X)} \rightarrow {C^{\rm R}_*(X)}$.

